<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>CafeFlow | Home</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <style>
      :root { color-scheme: dark; }
      body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 2rem; background: #0f1115; color: #e5e7eb; }
      .card { max-width: 720px; margin: 4rem auto; background: #1c1f26; border: 1px solid #2a2f3a; border-radius: 16px; padding: 24px; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 10px; background: #ff6b00; color: white; text-decoration: none; margin-right: 8px; }
      .muted { color: #9aa4b2; }
      code { background: #0b0d12; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 6px; }
      hr { border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #2a2f3a; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="card">
      <h1>✅ CafeFlow server is running</h1>
      <p class="muted">If you were seeing a blank page before, the server wasn’t running. It’s now up.</p>

      <h3>Quick links</h3>
      <p>
        <a class="btn" href="/admin/login">Admin Login</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/admin/register">Admin Register</a>
        <a class="btn" href="/admin/dashboard">Admin Dashboard</a>
      </p>
      <p class="muted">Note: Admin routes require their pages and auth to be set up. If you see 404, those pages aren’t added yet.</p>

      <hr />
      <p class="muted">Health check: <a href="/health">/health</a></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
